cs.DL, cs.IR, cs.WEB, cs.CR, cs.HC 

This paper discusses the challenges of archiving web resources, which falls under the category of digital libraries (cs.DL). The use of headless browsing clients and crawling strategies involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and web technologies (cs.WEB). The paper also discusses the performance of different crawling tools, which could be considered under computer networks (cs.CR). Finally, the paper discusses the usability of archived web resources, which could be considered under human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
